data.description: This property presents an ideal combination of convenience and modern living. With three bedrooms, it offers ample space for comfortable living.   Situated in the prime North Raleigh area, residents enjoy easy access to both Downtown Raleigh and RTP, making commuting a breeze.    The first floor boasts an entertainment room, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply relaxing with family and friends.   Additionally, there's an office space, providing a dedicated area for productivity and focus.    Impeccably maintained, this home shows like new, offering a fresh and inviting atmosphere for its occupants. Whether you're enjoying the vibrant city life or retreating to your private sanctuary, this property provides the perfect balance of location, functionality, and style.    Showings start on 4/20.
